Q.Difference between Flexbox and grid?
=>Both Flexbox and css grid has its own importance and should be used for
designing a web page.
=>grid  works for 2D alignment
=>Flexbox is good for space distribution

CSS grid
=>Grid Column:-The vertical line of grid items are called columns.
=>Grid Row:-The Horizontal line of grid items are called rows.
=>Grid Gaps:-The space between each Column/row are called gaps.(Column gap)(row gap)
=>Grid Lines:-The Line between columns are called columns lines.
              The Line between columns are called row lines.
